skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tweet info
des: Tweet Info gives you basic and relevant information about your Twitter Account, Alexa can tell you how many followers or a number of tweets you have posted since you have opened your account and also can tell you when was the day that you have created your account.
